lead_paragraph: Scores or perhaps hundreds of killings remain unsolved in Benghazi, Libya. But no victim has symbolized the crushed hopes of the Libyan uprising more than Salwa Bugaighis.

headline.main: The Brutal Silencing of a Woman at the Forefront of Libya’s Rebellion
